OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,FStalking laws in England are "slightly
OL,7,Fcallous" and crucial protection orders
OL,8,Ffor victims are not easy to obtain,
OL,9,FHome Office minister Jess Phillips has
OL,10,Fadmitted.
OL,12,FThe Under-Secretary of State for
OL,13,FSafeguarding and Violence Against
OL,14,FWomen and Girls admitted a
OL,15,F'fundamental problem' with the wording
OL,16,Fof the stalking laws.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
