OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777299067
OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,FCurrently laws in England put a large
OL,7,Fonus on the victim to prove they were
OL,8,Ffearful or distressed during stalking
OL,9,Fexperiences to secure higher sentences
OL,10,Fagainst perpetrators.
OL,12,FIt means that when victims are unaware
OL,13,Fthey are even being stalked it can
OL,14,Fmake it difficult to get the outcome
OL,15,Fthey may hope for.
OL,17,F"There is a fundamental problem with
OL,18,Fthe idea you have to prove distress,"
OL,19,Fthe minister admitted to ITV West
OL,20,FCountry.
OL,26,@yD@AOUzD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
