OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777299067
OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,F"Making victims jump through hoops
OL,7,Fabout how distressed they were on
OL,8,Fwhich day is a sort of slightly
OL,9,Fcallous way that our current laws are
OL,10,Fwritten."
OL,12,FShe went on to add there is also
OL,13,Fconfusion between stalking and
OL,14,Fharassment laws and that the process
OL,15,Ffor obtaining stalking protection
OL,16,Forders was not easy.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
