OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777299067
OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,FShe said it was part of the reason the
OL,7,Fgovernment had asked prominent British
OL,8,Fbarrister Richard Wright KC to
OL,9,Fundertake a review of stalking laws in
OL,10,FEngland.
OL,12,FAccording to figures obtained by the
OL,13,FONS, 1 in 5 women in the UK and 1 in
OL,14,F11 men say they have experienced
OL,15,Fstalking. But the prosecution rate
OL,16,Fremains low at around 1.4 per cent.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
