OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777299067
OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,FAsked what the government is doing to
OL,7,Ffix that, Ms Phillips said: "There's
OL,8,Fno one thing that will fix it all on
OL,9,Fits own. You have to take a series of
OL,10,Fdifferent actions."
OL,12,FShe said the actions included
OL,13,Fascertaining whether police and other
OL,14,Fagencies were able to handle stalking
OL,15,Fcases when they came up, if current
OL,16,Flaws were fit for purpose and making
OL,17,Fsure victims had the support they
OL,18,Fneeded to continue with complaints.
OL,26,@oD@]OUrD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
