OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777299067
OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,FResponding to claims that the police
OL,7,Fresponse to stalking was a postcode
OL,8,Flottery and that many forces claimed
OL,9,Fto need more funding, she said: "I
OL,10,Fwould be lying to you if I stood in
OL,11,Ffront of you and I said that you are
OL,12,Fgoing to get the exact same brilliant
OL,13,Fservice (across all forces).
OL,15,F"All of these things rely on
OL,16,Findividuals within those those forces
OL,17,Fand personnel and people with passion
OL,18,Fworking on it.
OL,26,@qD@aOUuD@IpmuD@[pnwD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777299067
OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,F"Of course, there needs to be funding
OL,7,Fallocated to it. But what I would also
OL,8,Fsay is it isn't just funding. Police
OL,9,Fforces need to think that stalking is
OL,10,Fa priority as well."
OL,12,FDespite the challenges, Ms Phillips
OL,13,Fsaid it was important for victims of
OL,14,Fstalking crimes to still come forward.
OL,16,FShe said: "What I would say is always
OL,17,Freport. Long before I was a lofty
OL,18,Fpolitician, I have suffered from
OL,19,Fstalking that I didn't report.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@TO]xD@KOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1777299067
OL,3,CJess Phillips admits a 'fundamental
OL,4,Cproblem' around current stalking laws
OL,6,F"Part of the pattern of stalking is
OL,7,Fyou made to feel a little bit like
OL,8,Fyou're going mad. It does that to you.
OL,10,F"I've seen too many cases where the
OL,11,Fpeople who didn't come forward ended
OL,12,Fup dead. So it's not to be undermined.
OL,14,F"To really change violence against
OL,15,Fwomen and girls and issues like
OL,16,Fstalking, we are going to have to
OL,17,Ffundamentally shift what is
OL,18,Fgenerations of normative behaviour
OL,19,Fabout how women don't trust the
OL,20,Fsystem, how women are made to feel
OL,21,Flike they make things up.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
